{"tid":303163,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【4月新番】 劍姬神聖譚 12","createTime":"2017-06-30T03:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T02:17:43.000Z","uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cda8d25d1417f8c26fba67f765df2c9d7c43cc5c","tid":303163,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fGRSpYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfGRSpYr.jpg&h=d01488a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正傳只有149句台詞的【劍姬】艾絲&middot;華倫斯坦。<br />\n以最強聞名的女劍士今天也和同伴們一起，<br />\n前往廣大的地下迷宮「地下城」。<br />\n腐朽成灰的龍的殘骸，隱藏於暗處的異常事態<br />\n在種種神秘的威脅來襲的深層域50階層，<br />\n艾絲呼喚疾風，在迷宮的黑暗中刻下一閃！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;之後來訪的是，與少年的「邂逅」<br />\n「那個&hellip;&hellip;你，沒事嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n在迷宮都市歐拉麗之地，<br />\n少女與少年的物語鮮烈地交錯！<br />\n<br />\n這是，另一個眷族的物語，<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;【劍姬神聖譚Sword Oratoria】&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原作：大森藤ノ<br />\n角色原案：灰村清孝、安田典生<br />\n監督：鈴木洋平<br />\n系列構成：白根秀樹<br />\n角色設計：木本茂樹<br />\n音樂：井內啟二<br />\n動畫製作：J.C.STAFF<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n艾絲&middot;華倫斯坦:大西沙織<br />\n蕾菲亞&middot;維里迪斯:木村珠莉<br />\n蒂奧娜&middot;席呂特:村川梨衣<br />\n蒂奧涅&middot;席呂特:高橋未奈美<br />\n洛基:久保由利香<br />\n芬恩&middot;蒂姆那:田村睦心<br />\n里維莉雅&middot;利歐斯&middot;阿爾弗:川澄綾子(正傳動畫版:種田梨沙)<br />\n貝爾&middot;克朗尼：松岡禎丞<br />\n赫斯緹雅：水瀨祈<br />\nviu逢星期五深夜 03:30更新[/quote]"},{"pid":"8abd6e74067b220efe698f99f81dbbfc0e187b98","tid":303163,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:11:51.000Z","msg":"連10,11都未睇<br />\n<br />\n今日趁得閒要補返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d720de03d074db43cf4260198b86fa967741c4f0","tid":303163,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"動畫Cut 到咁 艾絲都仲有5百幾句台詞"},{"pid":"3ad3d5263b708c80620979726922386e81617517","tid":303163,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"補返前兩集先<br />\n<br />\n10話<br />\n<br />\n垃圾<br />\n<br />\n11話<br />\n<br />\n有part絕對要吐糟 椿派不壞武嗰陣艾絲點會有份攞 製作組實在太唔認真<br />\n<br />\n51~58層有怪人派新種怪襲擊芬恩嗰邊又唔講<br />\n<br />\n然後明明加雷斯嗰邊打左8個鐘以上又提都唔提<br />\n<br />\n真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57e0868687ed82db14ef5e1a6e05a36f7a57eef","tid":303163,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jVJr6xgK04c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjVJr6xgK04c&d=jdE0CXUA4ZDiSTzF1B2RBhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0f9773f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jVJr6xgK04c</a><br />\n<br />\n角色歌"},{"pid":"907534f6840b029f385cf327ea211041392ea3ff","tid":303163,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T00:07:24.000Z","msg":"點解冇左中毒拎藥果段"},{"pid":"86cc55555fc9b51fd8d377d70dd1772d159dd4c9","tid":303163,"uid":120859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T01:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解冇左中毒拎藥果段</blockquote><br />\n都唔會有第二季架啦<br />\n求其啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟點做先可以做到咁underwhelming <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結局果度做mud野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477115c192be1394656aa919bc7b9dc88c5d519f","tid":303163,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:19:05.000Z","msg":"想問小說貝爾去到咩LV?"},{"pid":"46393f4e52a130945d55653a6b798e1f7d96263a","tid":303163,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問小說貝爾去到咩LV?</blockquote><br />\n4 實力上已經到5"},{"pid":"befef8f60988426cb27347c950786fe3ae1cdae5","tid":303163,"uid":41434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問小說貝爾去到咩LV?</blockquote><br />\n4 實力上已經到5</blockquote><br />\n加埋春雞 可以去洛基搵人隻揪都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c50c1cea0383e98b9de1e2ed59aee9997e9296","tid":303163,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問小說貝爾去到咩LV?</blockquote><br />\n4 實力上已經到5</blockquote><br />\n加埋春雞 可以去洛基搵人隻揪都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻邊個先"},{"pid":"e11f9b147916f739c2dddb15ccf9433981a8ea2a","tid":303163,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問小說貝爾去到咩LV?</blockquote><br />\n4 實力上已經到5</blockquote><br />\n加埋春雞 可以去洛基搵人隻揪都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻邊個先</blockquote><br />\n隻狼人 兩姊妹無問題啦<br />\n<br />\n狼人唔識並行詠唱打到佢仆街都得"},{"pid":"99b34613b5490606477397a1b0e8221ccf8eb4af","tid":303163,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問小說貝爾去到咩LV?</blockquote><br />\n4 實力上已經到5</blockquote><br />\n加埋春雞 可以去洛基搵人隻揪都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻邊個先</blockquote><br />\n隻狼人 兩姊妹無問題啦<br />\n<br />\n狼人唔識並行詠唱打到佢仆街都得</blockquote><br />\n不過狼人等同封左火焰閃電"},{"pid":"1e2d2cff7e4c6cc567ad2ceae0ebb01c7b824e72","tid":303163,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問小說貝爾去到咩LV?</blockquote><br />\n4 實力上已經到5</blockquote><br />\n加埋春雞 可以去洛基搵人隻揪都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻邊個先</blockquote><br />\n隻狼人 兩姊妹無問題啦<br />\n<br />\n狼人唔識並行詠唱打到佢仆街都得</blockquote><br />\n不過狼人等同封左火焰閃電</blockquote><br />\n唔係 假設唔係狼人偷襲而係對等打佢一定開唔到技"},{"pid":"b49685c0d380865a15f6528f2b9c15bb4791e052","tid":303163,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"最後果段先似主線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5949aba241efd0898702aff3a0ae042b8914025b","tid":303163,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 製作組係咪好憎劍姬，個個D技都畫到OK，係劍姬招風咁柒，明明係最後一擊黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW 中毒個part 係之後既事黎, 好似係"},{"pid":"e74ca746da27f82201fcc0826e6063c34a810d07","tid":303163,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:24:50.000Z","msg":"睇完。<br />\n<br />\n不得不讚 今集真係超水準（比起前11話）<br />\n<br />\n完全做得出最終戰嗰種緊張感<br />\n<br />\n一見boss詠唱即刻要搵人斷佢 團體合作都做到出黎<br />\n<br />\n加雷斯同里維莉亞中招個part都有<br />\n<br />\n還原度好高 本來落58層做到咁糞已經0期望<br />\n<br />\n點知最後一集俾到驚喜我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好希望本傳有2季 非常 非常想睇第9~12卷劇情<br />\n<br />\n貝爾同洛基眷族對立 以及牛妹戰都係近幾年睇過既輕小說中最燃既一部分<br />\n<br />\n但更加希望唔好俾白根做 事實證明呢條友係原作破壞機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今集里維莉亞又係莫名地畫得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/131412_316a56a5a793f42d0a705518ba554359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F131412_316a56a5a793f42d0a705518ba554359.jpg&h=3118ecd3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/131412_79ca6f03f63784cac55be84c015f4289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F131412_79ca6f03f63784cac55be84c015f4289.jpg&h=88bb9b75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n芬恩既狂化技都有做出黎 幾型 抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/131449_fbe7707724531a5137d1e523513ecf0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F131449_fbe7707724531a5137d1e523513ecf0e.jpg&h=0b28f6d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢part疑似係芬恩發動左魔法（外傳第8卷先公佈）<br />\n一招就打斷左墮落精靈施法<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">魔法：T&iacute;r na n&oacute;g（ティル・ナ・ノーグ）：投擲魔法，魔法威力會按照等級和全能力值（包括潛在值）累加， 只能發動一次，冷卻時間為24小時</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/131823_877348ecc14bf77ee0d73c543188e307.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F131823_877348ecc14bf77ee0d73c543188e307.jpg&h=f6caad35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/131824_f4fb22982423100d2aeaa8d3080be810.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F131824_f4fb22982423100d2aeaa8d3080be810.jpg&h=b7103f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蕾菲亞兩次救場 今集MVP<br />\n等你班友仲成日話佢廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlv3已經做到主力軍 雖然唔夠兔仔黎不過前途無可限量<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/131955_4f90e88368304574ba7cb1a8b57e8045.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F131955_4f90e88368304574ba7cb1a8b57e8045.jpg&h=030674c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/131955_e792ed846bc3054bd588de78b5dae75b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F131955_e792ed846bc3054bd588de78b5dae75b.jpg&h=fb412932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最尾芙蕾雅同菲爾維絲仲有鏡頭出 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/132125_cf6b3eea3f7bc39fb665ca4fa1406b4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F132125_cf6b3eea3f7bc39fb665ca4fa1406b4e.jpg&h=d791e341&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/132126_cf6b3eea3f7bc39fb665ca4fa1406b4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F132126_cf6b3eea3f7bc39fb665ca4fa1406b4e.jpg&h=34d854e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蕾菲亞識過肩摔應該係外傳9既事 呢度搬左黎前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/132232_aa85cb0b52287ec84dbdf8851bb5c69e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F132232_aa85cb0b52287ec84dbdf8851bb5c69e.jpg&h=378b8be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw今集艾絲既風依然係小畫家級作畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/132324_45cc52c5ba2f96b4d166f1d4c815e7bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F132324_45cc52c5ba2f96b4d166f1d4c815e7bf.jpg&h=5e426682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 今集我俾85/100<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全季評分60/100 有50分係愛作加成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4970440f9162c19b805fbc2dbb227d64af020808","tid":303163,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"我俾50分<br />\n20 作畫唔叫好差<br />\n30分大西+原作愛"},{"pid":"fe1ed75cb1dd9fa097cea33e4cc19ef35a454954","tid":303163,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我俾50分<br />\n20 作畫唔叫好差<br />\n30分大西+原作愛</blockquote><br />\n前面有幾集真係崩到無眼睇<br />\n<br />\n都唔明點解本書咁賣得都唔揼本落去整好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c49b89fb3afe6f3a8d020c9e05b662b49cf2746","tid":303163,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:43:59.000Z","msg":"睇下月尾有冇咩新figure公佈先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62844bf1ca2165943d9484fd1cfd35efd3caedd0","tid":303163,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下月尾有冇咩新figure公佈先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/134456_66fbbcf5b4845bae93abee1d978cd6c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F134456_66fbbcf5b4845bae93abee1d978cd6c4.jpg&h=ce12749f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bcf5d9eb630b8491fa1ce42115f7c1c41141ebd","tid":303163,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇下月尾有冇咩新figure公佈先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/134456_66fbbcf5b4845bae93abee1d978cd6c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F134456_66fbbcf5b4845bae93abee1d978cd6c4.jpg&h=ce12749f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我反而想問 貝爾有冇機會出 figure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b47ad567e9b0414c2c791cb619998198a0341d6","tid":303163,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:21:43.000Z","msg":"等緊d可動<br />\n出極都係神大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2450505aa2025a4aa16f4f321bf3814df412a05f","tid":303163,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等緊d可動<br />\n出極都係神大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔鐘意乳繩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想要琉figure"},{"pid":"d4b0c3aac96ab0d30dcebc573c5def0d545d4a85","tid":303163,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補返前兩集先<br />\n<br />\n10話<br />\n<br />\n垃圾<br />\n<br />\n11話<br />\n<br />\n有part絕對要吐糟 椿派不壞武嗰陣艾絲點會有份攞 製作組實在太唔認真<br />\n<br />\n51~58層有怪人派新種怪襲擊芬恩嗰邊又唔講<br />\n<br />\n然後明明加雷斯嗰邊打左8個鐘以上又提都唔提<br />\n<br />\n真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係蕾菲亞跌落去果陣幫伯特殺隻強化種都唔見左啦<br />\n明明製作組放棄劍姬劇情都要夾硬刷蕾菲亞存在感<br />\n但係蕾菲亞真係進步果一場竟然唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b73fbd9c49aff864fc1fca41c4a059abc28a759","tid":303163,"uid":20665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"有無人話我知入地下城前有人要佢係59層戴條鏈有咩用, 好似無發揮過作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2e8a6a91fde500478c884b584500e364b4803a","tid":303163,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人話我知入地下城前有人要佢係59層戴條鏈有咩用, 好似無發揮過作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係被公會個神睇59層發生咩事"},{"pid":"0f84d6bc3c70c115c4274603e998194e08d1c295","tid":303163,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無人話我知入地下城前有人要佢係59層戴條鏈有咩用, 好似無發揮過作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係被公會個神睇59層發生咩事</blockquote><br />\n正確黎講係個從者<br />\n條鏈上面粒水晶,會將影像同聲音傳送去水晶球<br />\n用途係偷拍劍姬沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid